\u0026#39;s invested in Google\u0026#39;s app ecosystem, you\u0026#39;ll know that the brand has a lot of different projects going on at one time, and a lot of them might not get updated as often as they should. With \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/google-calendar-android-gets-long-awaited-dedicated-tasks-view/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eTasks seeing integration into Google Calendar\u003c/a\u003e, we think it\u0026#39;s only a matter of time before \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/tasks-next-app-in-google-graveyard-editorial/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eTasks ends up in the graveyard\u003c/a\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n                \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"a04b-4bcb-abe5955cb00b\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/tasks-next-app-in-google-graveyard-editorial/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/google-may-be-moving-its-tasks-app-into-calendar.jpg\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/google-may-be-moving-its-tasks-app-into-calendar.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/google-may-be-moving-its-tasks-app-into-calendar.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/google-may-be-moving-its-tasks-app-into-calendar.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/google-may-be-moving-its-tasks-app-into-calendar.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/google-may-be-moving-its-tasks-app-into-calendar.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/google-may-be-moving-its-tasks-app-into-calendar.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/google-may-be-moving-its-tasks-app-into-calendar.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/google-may-be-moving-its-tasks-app-into-calendar.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"android phone showing google calendar app on yellow background\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/google-may-be-moving-its-tasks-app-into-calendar.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/wm/2024/12/google-may-be-moving-its-tasks-app-into-calendar.jpg\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eWith that said, there\u0026#39;s been more \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/google-tasks-completion-dates-upcoming-update/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eactivity on Tasks recently\u003c/a\u003e, potentially indicating that Google is still looking to keep the app alive for the time being. Today, Google Tasks is getting another addition in the form of incomplete counts that now show up in lists to provide a constant reminder of the things you need to get done. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"unfinished-to-dos-are-now-a-constant-reminder\"\u003e\n                        Unfinished to-dos are now a constant reminder\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n                \n    \n    \n    \n                \n    \n                \n        \n                                                                                \n                                                                                                                        \n                            \n    \n    \n    \n    \u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot-2025-03-28-at-8-01-53-am.png\" data-img-desc=\"\u0026#34;Source:\u0026amp;nbsp;\u0026lt;a href=\\\u0026#34;https:\\/\\/9to5google.com\\/2025\\/03\\/27\\/google-tasks-counts\\/\\\u0026#34; rel=\\\u0026#34;noopener noreferrer nofollow\\\u0026#34; target=\\\u0026#34;_blank\\\u0026#34;\u0026gt;9to5Google\u0026lt;\\/a\u0026gt;\u0026#34;\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" dat